<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
    <section class="rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-300 via-emerald-300 to-lime-200 p-8 text-slate-900 shadow-[0_28px_90px_rgba(56,189,248,0.18)] lg:p-10">
        <p class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-white/40 bg-white/45 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-700">Welcome Back</p>
        <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight">Masuk ke pusat aktivitas lingkungan komunitas Anda.</h1>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
            Login untuk memantau kontribusi, melihat status verifikasi, dan mengelola aktivitas warga dalam satu dashboard yang lebih terstruktur.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/40 bg-white/45 p-5">
                <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Track with accountability</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">Setiap log sampah memiliki bukti, status review, dan dampak poin yang jelas.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/40 bg-white/45 p-5">
                <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Built for RT/RW workflow</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">Data warga dan validasi admin dirancang agar cocok untuk operasional komunitas kecil.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/95 p-8 shadow-[0_18px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] backdrop-blur lg:p-10">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-100 pb-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-600">Sign In</p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Login to Eco-Pulse</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Gunakan akun yang sudah terdaftar untuk mengakses dashboard warga atau panel admin.</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/login" method="POST" class="mt-8 space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Password</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" placeholder="Minimum 8 characters" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="w-full rounded-full bg-emerald-700 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-[0_12px_30px_rgba(21,128,61,0.24)] transition hover:bg-emerald-800">Sign In to Dashboard</button>
        </form>

        <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-5 py-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
            Belum punya akun? <a href="/register" class="font-bold text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800">Buat akun baru di halaman register</a>.
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
